metadata.name: DuDuLab #1
metadata.description:
Rebellion bear

Age: 7-15

Background: DUDU was adopted by the grandmother because he had no parents since he was a child. Because of his special status, he is always excluded and discriminated against by his peers. He is also often bullied by pranks. In order to protect himself, Xiaoxiong embarked on the path of a bad boy, and at the same time he began to question and rebel against this society.
